{
  "text": "PCA on covariance matrix was performed on the data matrix (bacterial communities as rows and bands as columns). This method provided an ordination of bacterial or fungal communities and of the encoded bands, which were plotted in two dimensions based on the scores in the first two principal components. PCA was performed using the ADE-4 software [CITATION_1] .",
  "citation_candidates": [
